 />\n又乜9都做唔到<br />\n未嘗唔係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77bee262fd0b6c3ab83d0b6a4e8c6a942b5d8db","tid":1262931,"uid":65686,"like":231,"dislike":0,"score":231,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"即係已經回應左訴求:<br />\n1 撤回修例❌暫緩<br />\n2 不檢控示威者❌ 唔得，會干預司法<br />\n3 取消暴動定性❌ 至少5個義士暴動，陸續有來<br />\n4 追究警方責任❌ 唔會獨立調查，照舊監警會查<br />\n5 特首林鄭月娥下台❌ 我死唔去"},{"pid":"b610ad05b3bc7397d59fd58aa6bcb545ee0a987c","tid":1262931,"uid":144018,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"真係好打得<br />\n打走哂啲訴求然後仲要打返你兩拳話係你唔岩唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbf8d94a293c5b15e5ff2cf9e1cce8ff5dec403","tid":1262931,"uid":8171,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"剛復自用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />闖出大禍仲死不悔改，社會繼續撕裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edee2e610ca960b2c17b088f9861d2f60439faf","tid":1262931,"uid":42675,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"民主之母留守香港我一定支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0029217e23d0df8072a32d6e6fa1ead950948af2","tid":1262931,"uid":263652,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"即係話，只要搵到唔洗佢辭職既下台方法就得啦<br />\n咁真係有好多方法既⋯"},{"pid":"7a94db2900c4910fad959e7b2e7f26d643959f85","tid":1262931,"uid":38610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:40:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a2dcbcbbbafd640b1f7195a18e5f57b6ae9440b4","tid":1262931,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n