唔係好打得 人地話唔辭職<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"咁起訴示威者又唔係針對示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用你個爛鬼監警會投訴打記者都唔撚理人啦 仲想有機會查開槍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"屌！真係好L燥！！！"},{"pid":"2fc3d8e3408cc42529dd1d250873a1ebfffca0bb","tid":1262931,"uid":161709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea67fe2254b2fd7a236a612dd47d34e7cbd7903e","tid":1262931,"uid":599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"71 又要100萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"300+1萬得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4872a67e1bc50ac71b60055558245c8fca4cfa","tid":1262931,"uid":35155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:05:18.000Z","msg":"獨立委員會好撚基本都唔肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a7ccf83a4e1113788899493bf98b06ae18c86a","tid":1262931,"uid":146390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆幾時死"},{"pid":"68d4fcca313674cb3abc12164603fe8606613f79","tid":1262931,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef455a34d933df6a034e76db17159f1e8794846","tid"